---
import DraftLayout from '../../layouts/DraftLayout.astro';
---
<DraftLayout title="Writings — Subtle Somatics" description="Reflections and insights from the path of subtle somatic unfolding." activeNav="writings">

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-inner">
      <p class="eyebrow">Writings</p>
      <h1 class="reveal">Reflections from the path</h1>
      <p class="reveal" data-delay="100">Insights from the path of subtle somatic unfolding — where the body speaks and we learn to listen.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="writings-grid">
      <article class="writing-card card-shine reveal" data-delay="0">
        <div class="writing-badge">Coming soon</div>
        <h3>On the Breath Behind the Breath</h3>
        <p class="writing-excerpt">This is the work of becoming intimate with nuance: reading the breath behind the breath, the movement beneath stillness, the sound inside silence.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="writing-card card-shine reveal" data-delay="150">
        <div class="writing-badge">Coming soon</div>
        <h3>No Adjustment is Imposed</h3>
        <p class="writing-excerpt">Instead, the inner terrain is offered space to self-organize according to its original intelligence.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="writing-card card-shine reveal" data-delay="300">
        <div class="writing-badge">Coming soon</div>
        <h3>Returning to the Body as Field</h3>
        <p class="writing-excerpt">To practice subtle somatics is to return to the body not as vessel, but as a field — alive, aware, and already knowing.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Subscribe -->
  <section class="section-surface">
    <div class="section subscribe-section">
      <div class="subscribe-inner reveal">
        <h2 class="text-center">Stay in the field</h2>
        <p class="text-center subscribe-sub">Subscribe to be notified when new writings are published — reflections on embodiment, presence, and the subtle path.</p>
        <form class="subscribe-form" action="https://formsubmit.co/connect@subtlesomatics.space" method="POST">
          <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="New subscriber — Writings (draft)" />
          <input type="hidden" name="_captcha" value="false" />
          <input type="hidden" name="_next" value="https://subtlesomatics.space/draft/writings" />
          <input type="text" name="_honey" style="display:none" />
          <div class="subscribe-row">
            <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="your@email.com" required aria-label="Email address" />
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-filled">Notify Me</button>
          </div>
          <p class="subscribe-note">No spam. Unsubscribe anytime.</p>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</DraftLayout>

<style>
  .page-hero { background: var(--bg-surface); padding: 10rem 2rem 6rem; text-align: center; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .page-hero-inner { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .page-hero h1 { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .page-hero p { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 1.15rem; margin: 0 auto; }
  .eyebrow { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }

  /* Writings grid */
  .writings-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2.5rem;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .writing-card {
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    position: relative;
    transition: border-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
  }
  .writing-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--border-hover);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }
  .writing-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    border: 1px solid var(--accent);
    padding: 0.2rem 0.7rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }
  .writing-card h3 {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 2vw, 1.6rem);
  }
  .writing-excerpt {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: none;
  }

  /* Subscribe */
  .subscribe-section { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .subscribe-inner { text-align: center; }
  .subscribe-inner h2 { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .subscribe-sub {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }
  .subscribe-form { max-width: 450px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .subscribe-row {
    display: flex; gap: 0.75rem;
  }
  .subscribe-row input[type="email"] {
    flex: 1;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1rem;
    padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-weight: 300;
    transition: border-color 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
  }
  .subscribe-row input[type="email"]:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px var(--accent-glow), 0 0 16px var(--accent-glow);
  }
  .subscribe-note {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-top: 0.8rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .writings-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; max-width: 500px; }
    .subscribe-row { flex-direction: column; }
  }
</style>
